@IlyaGazman For info on pull requests, see [this](https://yangsu.github.io/pull-request-tutorial/) (or any other) general info tutorial and [this](https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/wiki/Contributing) libGDX specific page for contributors. You don't have to get it right the first time - that is what code review is for, so don't worry about it too much.

@shatterblast: By warning, I meant this line:  
`WARNING: Could not open/create prefs root node Software\JavaSoft\Prefs at root 0x80000002. Windows RegCreateKeyEx(...) returned error code 5.`,
which has nothing to do with any networking and everything to do with [windows registry](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/api/winreg/nf-winreg-regcreatekeyexa).
